sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant W as Web
  participant S as Service
  participant D as DB
  U->>W: Submit order
  W->>+S: validateAndCreate()
  alt valid
    par write order
      S->>+D: insert order
      D-->>-S: order id
    and publish event
      S-->>S: enqueue event
    end
    S-->>W: 201 Created
  else invalid
    S-->>W: 400 Bad Request
  end
  W-->>U: response
